  - https://git.disroot.org/AXP.OS/build/raw/branch/axp/Scripts/LineageOS-22.2/CVE_Patchers/android_kernel_oneplus_sm8250.sh
  - https://git.disroot.org/AXP.OS/kernel_patches

  Selection method:
  - start from the AXP.OS script entries relevant to the local patched kernel
  - keep the existing checked subset already carried in this repo
  - test omitted script entries against the current patched kernel tree
  - keep only the additional patches that still apply cleanly in script order as
    one cumulative series
  - exclude subtree-only patches that need git apply --directory=... because
    nix-kernelsu-builder's kernelPatches hook applies patches from repo root

  Result:
  - 155 script-order patches currently apply cleanly to the local android_kernel_samsung_sm8250 lineage-23.2 (4.19.325)
*/
